{"tid":450044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登賣廣告 賣到有片","createTime":"2017-10-27T18:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T18:49:37.000Z","uid":132605,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d20759a499a0f88d7179b48660935c05f2d8ff1","tid":450044,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/022254_9a938bde9458c097d8615affcbd052b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F022254_9a938bde9458c097d8615affcbd052b4.jpg&h=9574daad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賣廣告維持個ser運作唔係問題 <br />\n而家賣撚埋影片廣告一定收唔撚少錢啦<br />\n開始賺取更多錢 而去搞呢個壇 <br />\n慢慢走上早洩o既路 <br />\n出街用data就一定要down你條19片<br />\n當初咁多位會員點解要轉黎你個壇呀<br />\n就係因為早洩 為賺取更多金錢 漠視會員訴求<br />\n而家你同佢有咩分別"},{"pid":"dd83b787721c01fd6dd6de71c14e145552437397","tid":450044,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2951f606584d0e6a1f3a7133ed0bd106f8ad5d3c","tid":450044,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347d6731efa5788e20b9c1872073dd513febf023","tid":450044,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f720d83d95874a8922162660e5c7fe1dbbac493","tid":450044,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"連尻住為左賺錢可以去到幾盡？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/390052/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://l